   1 | # PySR symbolic benchmark: Universal amyloid aggregation kinetics
   2 | # Multi-dataset fitting across ALL disease-relevant non-inhibited proteins
   3 | # Usage: skydiscover-run initial_program.py evaluator.py -c config.yaml -s adaevolve|evox
